FBIS3-17868 "drsov061_v_94008" FBIS-SOV-94-061 Document Type:Daily Report 29 Mar 1994 Lithuania New Director for National Minorities Department LD2903214194 Vilnius Radio Vilnius International Service in Lithuanian 2100 GMT 29 Mar 94 LD2903214194 Vilnius Radio Vilnius International Service Language: Lithuanian Article Type:BFN [Text] Alfonsas Sveinys has been appointed general director of the Department of Regional Problems and National Minorities attached to the Lithuanian Government. The Department of Regional Problems and National Minorities has been formed after the reorganization of the Department of Nationalities and of the State Commission for Regional Problems. Sveinys had been deputy director of the Department of nationalities.
